Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.35,0:00:14.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.57,0:00:19.62,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pu-Re-Mi-A-Mu...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.96,0:00:22.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiyo-Ko-Re... To.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.91,0:00:24.54,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Woah! You actually read it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.54,0:00:25.79,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was amazing, Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.39,0:00:28.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mandom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.07,0:00:30.15,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mandom?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.15,0:00:34.83,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By mastering the katakana syllables we were \Nsupposed to learn after summer vacation,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:36.81,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've become a little more adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.16,0:00:40.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything appears beautiful to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.74,0:00:47.56,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations! Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.98,0:00:42.88,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what it means to grow up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.53,0:00:47.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense the world's blessings \Nupon my newly-attained self.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.05,0:00:49.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mandom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.20,0:00:50.73,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did she pick that up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.16,0:00:53.65,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's try one a mite harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.65,0:00:54.57,MX Signs 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Goto Milk
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.28,0:00:56.32,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! Can you read the arrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.57,0:00:56.32,MX Signs 3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Akekuchi{\i0}\N(Open Here)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.64,0:00:58.82,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It says, A-Ke..."Ro."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.82,0:01:00.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Woah, yer amazing, Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.84,0:01:05.00,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't learn that kana 'til \Nthird term... or even second grade!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:07.94,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you read it right, \Nthis milk's yer prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.36,0:01:09.79,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.20,0:01:13.31,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go show everyone how you can read that kana!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.74,0:01:17.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Children really do grow up fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.47,0:01:21.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I never thought she \Nwas that into studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.35,0:01:24.15,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What suddenly motivated her?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.63,0:01:26.89,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Three guesses, first two don't count.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.89,0:01:28.06,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.17,0:01:29.94,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.37,0:01:31.71,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.71,0:01:33.61,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, can you read this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.61,0:01:37.61,MX Signs 4,,0000,0000,0000,,Mimei Market
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.33,0:01:36.19,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It says, "akekuchi."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:03:00.70,Barakamon Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Barakamon
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:17.96,Barakamon Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitonmochi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:17.96,Barakamon Title Translation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(480,1)}Translation:\NMochi Thrown in Celebration
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:21.57,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I just mailed it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.57,0:03:23.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Submit it to the Tokyo Kasho Exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.57,0:03:26.01,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Feeling confident?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.86,0:03:28.77,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my current self's calligraphy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:33.48,MX Calligraphy 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-Hearted
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:31.47,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't send it if I wasn't confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.47,0:03:33.48,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't wait to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.78,0:03:35.68,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:38.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all out of ink.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.35,0:03:42.31,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.31,0:03:44.03,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where can I buy ink?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.56,0:03:45.89,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinoshita General Store?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.19,0:03:50.28,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good t'see ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.11,0:03:52.53,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for helping me move in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:56.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take yer time lookin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.74,0:04:01.10,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,There's just about everything here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:07.39,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheap candy... They never let me eat \Nany as a kid, since it was bad for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.32,0:04:12.02,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,With Naru coming over to play, \NI should have some on hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.32,0:04:16.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru likes Kanro hard candy and Choco-Bats.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:17.48,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she psychic!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:18.86,MX Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Squid on a Stick
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:22.65,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll buy some in bulk...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.02,0:04:25.72,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, then other kids gonna come...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:30.09,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:32.95,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cheap, so a peek wouldn't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:35.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.98,0:04:37.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.68,0:04:39.04,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Needles?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.79,0:04:45.80,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Augh! Sorry, I'll pick them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:04:57.04,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.04,0:04:58.64,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.64,0:05:00.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:02.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You done swept the floor for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.67,0:05:06.40,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't bend over lately \Non account of back pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.98,0:05:09.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was mighty helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.05,0:05:11.80,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it because you're \Ncarrying that poodle?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.80,0:05:13.26,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:16.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,'Scuze me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.45,0:05:17.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:20.73,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mighty hot out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:22.88,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good t'see ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:25.67,MX Main Dialog - down,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bad back a'mite bettah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:25.67,MX Main Dialog - up,,0000,0000,0000,,Translation: Is your back doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:27.63,MX Main Dialog - down,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wha' you a'heah foah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:27.63,MX Main Dialog - up,,0000,0000,0000,,Translation: What did you come to buy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:29.60,MX Main Dialog - up,,0000,0000,0000,,Translation: Do you have any thread({\i1}ito{\i0})?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.84,0:05:31.85,MX Main Dialog - up,,0000,0000,0000,,Translation: Yes, it hurts({\i1}ita{\i0}).
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:36.77,MX Main Dialog - up,,0000,0000,0000,,Translation: Do you have any thread?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:38.73,MX Main Dialog - up,,0000,0000,0000,,Translation: Yes, it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:42.19,MX Main Dialog - up,,0000,0000,0000,,Translation: Doesn't it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:43.98,MX Main Dialog - up,,0000,0000,0000,,Translation: Yes, it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:49.32,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, by "{\i1}ito{\i0}" you mean this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:52.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Thassit! Thassit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:53.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was askin' for those.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:57.37,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But she kept sayin' "{\i1}itaka{\i0}", "{\i1}itaka{\i0}"!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:06:01.55,MX Main Dialog - down,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ol' biddy heah got right bad eah'swell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:06:03.92,MX Main Dialog - up,,0000,0000,0000,,Translation: The old hag has bad ears too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.55,0:06:03.92,MX Main Dialog - down,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:13.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you gettin' so angry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:15.78,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right, ink.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:17.68,MX Signs 5,,0000,0000,0000,,Many-Many Ink Drops
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:22.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. You ended up letting me take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:24.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:25.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can always grind an ink stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.87,0:06:28.86,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This does help, I have a deadline soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:32.01,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I remember \Nabout you drawing manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.01,0:06:34.58,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!! My work is nothing that great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.09,0:06:37.33,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing to be ashamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:39.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We both know about the fun \Nof drawing and writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.47,0:06:41.62,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.89,0:06:44.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:50.65,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you... please read my manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:55.25,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I plan to submit it to a boys' magazine,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.25,0:06:57.64,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but I would like to hear \Nsomeone's frank opinion first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.22,0:07:01.55,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no expert on manga, so I \Ncouldn't give you any pointers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:02.57,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.57,0:07:04.36,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked because it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.58,0:07:07.48,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want someone who knows the fun \Nof drawing and writing to read it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:09.64,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I welcome your feedback.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.64,0:07:11.97,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, if you insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:19.71,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a striking introduction?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.64,0:07:23.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this for a horror magazine?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.05,0:07:24.29,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, a boys' magazine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:26.62,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something odd about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.69,0:07:28.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:30.97,MX Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Splort
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:32.80,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't it have more of the \Nusual boys' magazine stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:32.80,MX Handwritten 2,,0000,0000,0000,,The one whose name \Nis written bursts apart?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:32.80,MX Handwritten 3,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call it the \N"Snuff Note."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:34.93,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like friendship, hard work...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:36.26,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you crazy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.52,0:07:40.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I sent in a typical "honor and justice" \Nmanga, nobody would read it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.05,0:07:42.83,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blood! Flesh! Entrails exploding!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.83,0:07:44.28,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The righteous getting crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.28,0:07:45.63,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A protagonist on the dark side!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:48.69,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A complex bromance with a close \Nfriend who's actually the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:51.70,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A heroine who naturally fades \Nout after just one chapter!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:53.41,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, children will be—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:57.49,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Society demands story elements \Nit has never seen before!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:08:02.16,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Like having the heroine's best \Nfriend's grandpa as the final boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.36,0:08:07.63,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, considering the current \Ntrends, I guess it's a good manga—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.98,0:08:09.76,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please read it to the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.00,0:08:11.61,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then give me your impressions!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.61,0:08:13.01,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's no good, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:16.36,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be honest, even if you don't \Nthink I can handle the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.36,0:08:17.35,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.96,0:08:20.56,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't really want to hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:28.59,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Read these to understand manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.17,0:08:35.73,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not getting involved \Nwith manga artists ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:38.03,MX Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Many-Many Ink Drops
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:46.67,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd only told Miwa-chan that I planned \Nto be a manga artist someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:52.32,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,But then I got carried away and \Neven showed him my manuscript!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.21,0:08:57.26,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll I do if Sensei tells \Nthe villagers about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.52,0:08:59.73,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike Naru...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:08:59.73,MX Flashback 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tama does manga!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.73,0:09:02.81,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,...he'd have actual credibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.01,0:09:06.65,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole village will find out I'm a geek!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.03,0:09:09.33,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,A complex bromance with a close \Nfriend who's actually the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.33,0:09:12.04,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,A heroine who naturally fades out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:14.19,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,They might not just think I'm a geek...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.19,0:09:14.70,MX Signs - Def,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fujoshi{\i0} (Rotten Girl):
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:15.49,MX Signs - Def,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fujoshi{\i0} (Rotten Girl): a woman who prefers \Nnovels and manga that depict male-male romances.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.79,0:09:17.16,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll think I'm a {\i1}fujoshi{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.49,0:09:16.03,MX Signs - Def,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fujoshi{\i0} (Rotten Girl): a woman who prefers novels and manga that depict male-male romances.\NRelated: BL (Boys Love), Yaoi, Fudanshi(Rotten Boy)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:17.16,MX Signs - Def,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fujoshi{\i0} (Rotten Girl): a woman who prefers novels and manga that depict male-male romances.\NRelated:  BL (Boys Love), Yaoi, Fudanshi(Rotten Boy)\NFormula: Girl Who Likes Manga ≠ Fujoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.96,0:09:20.59,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't happen! \NI just love manga, is all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.59,0:09:22.36,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My interests are purely {\i1}literary{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:25.25,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not some vulgar fujoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:29.60,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}must{\i0} make that clear...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:33.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. I made today's dinner too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.66,0:09:35.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... thanks again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.92,0:09:38.16,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Something happen? You don't look so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:42.52,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, just thinking about how girls \Nthese days can be really passionate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:46.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And how I have to grind \Nall my ink from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.30,0:09:47.73,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got me down...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:51.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! So you couldn't buy ink? Thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:52.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Thought so"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:56.55,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They have penmanship homework for summer \Nvacation, so ink sells out right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:57.49,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.07,0:10:00.03,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought you this worn-out \Nbottle we had at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,0:10:04.45,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't clear up the misunderstanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.45,0:10:06.42,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,and get falsely accused of being a fujoshi,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.42,0:10:08.85,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll no longer be able \Nto live in this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.85,0:10:13.81,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell him, "When I said I wanted to be \Na manga artist, I really meant a {\i0}novelist{\i1}."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:19.89,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Could I have mistakenly lent \Nhim my most secret book?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:19.89,MX Signs 6,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}{\fs24}Overtime Lovers\N\N{\fs20}Sandro Tamura\N\N\N\N{\fs22\i1}"Huh? You're still here?!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.59,0:10:23.69,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened my first year of middle school...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.69,0:10:26.96,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Tama, you got some manga \Nfrom one of your cousins.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.96,0:10:28.52,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.93,0:10:31.44,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Tama sure does love manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:39.78,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? Two men doing that?! Ewww!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:43.24,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm traumatized for life!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:44.99,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,That's filthy, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.63,0:10:48.37,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Grown-ups are all dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:52.96,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Peek...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:58.67,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,So that I'd never forget what occurred \Nthat day, I've secured that manga!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:01.54,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I keep it separate from the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.54,0:11:03.36,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,so I couldn't have \Naccidentally lent it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.36,0:11:07.64,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I must protect my \Nreputation as a proper, literary girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.94,0:11:09.39,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:21.41,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, thanks for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.87,0:11:23.94,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect my foot to slip...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:27.04,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay, just get your \Nbalance back already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:29.89,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so happy about the ink, \Nthat I got a little dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:33.04,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna conk your \Nhead and die at some point!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:35.21,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, the champon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:35.21,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:36.69,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:36.77,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.69,0:11:39.04,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,You've brought champon a lot lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.77,0:11:40.62,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.04,0:11:40.95,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,We got noodles as a midsummer gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.95,0:11:42.32,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I must finish my manuscript.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.73,0:11:44.78,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Manuscript...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:47.38,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Manuscri...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:49.12,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Manu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.91,0:11:51.09,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.93,0:11:59.82,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid, stupid adolescence!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.91,0:12:02.73,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.73,0:12:04.16,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.54,0:12:06.43,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That writing was a masterpiece!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.43,0:12:08.16,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way it could've failed to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.93,0:12:17.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.41,0:12:22.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! Let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.58,0:12:25.97,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this stagnant air?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.48,0:12:31.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck's {\i1}that{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:34.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.20,0:12:35.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yer makin' gloom-fumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.16,0:12:41.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he mutterin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.38,0:12:44.57,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei says he got second place \Nin the calligraphy contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.00,0:12:48.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah... he was talkin' about \Nbein' in a calligraphy exhibit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.09,0:12:49.85,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't second place still pretty great?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.89,0:12:56.94,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He says, first place went to \Nan eighteen-year-old newbie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.82,0:13:01.85,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What, yer sulkin' 'cause you \Nlost to someone younger?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:03.72,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:03.72,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"That's all"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.14,0:13:07.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how much time and \Nenergy I put into that writing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.31,0:13:10.48,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I even went without sleep to finish it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.48,0:13:13.35,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've fallen behind some guy who \Nstarted calligraphy only yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:17.15,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd be able to write good \Ncalligraphy if I stayed on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:19.55,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But now I'm paying for having taken it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.08,0:13:22.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I never should've come to this stupid place!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.87,0:13:24.02,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now wait, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.02,0:13:25.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Miwa-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.05,0:13:27.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.67,0:13:29.57,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like our timing was bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.57,0:13:30.79,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll come back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.67,0:13:36.67,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn' you give him what for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.67,0:13:39.58,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He even said we were holdin' him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:41.70,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei has a lot of pride,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.70,0:13:45.22,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so using logic on him will \Njust make him more depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.98,0:13:47.71,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave it to Naru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.27,0:13:49.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:53.74,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn' Miwa-nee and Tama \Nleave unhappy with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.32,0:13:55.68,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.41,0:13:58.81,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even middle-school kids worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.81,0:14:00.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I really am pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:03.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, it's just so vexing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:06.74,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Without calligraphy, I have \Nnothing of value to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.87,0:14:10.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But since I didn't win, I'm worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:14.83,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, are you havin' fun right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.51,0:14:19.32,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ain't, then let's go play!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.26,0:14:26.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's carrying grocery bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.18,0:14:27.37,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.37,0:14:28.83,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mochi-picking!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.83,0:14:30.70,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know 'bout it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:33.01,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, yer a stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:33.76,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.95,0:14:37.77,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the thing where you toss \Nmochi after building a house, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:39.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never done it, but \NI still know that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.21,0:14:41.95,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A house?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:44.40,MX Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Catch
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.72,0:14:48.72,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's mochi-picking's for a boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.72,0:14:50.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna pick a bunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.08,0:14:53.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yer mighty late, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.46,0:14:55.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready, they're throwin' soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:57.33,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, what's this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:59.54,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta-folks' new boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.97,0:15:01.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kenta-folks"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.10,0:15:03.00,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:05.88,MX Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenmaru
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:07.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta! That's a mighty fine boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.35,0:15:09.88,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,'Course it is! It's called "Kenmaru"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:11.35,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kenmaru"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.35,0:15:15.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's actually good luck to name \Na boat after the eldest daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.10,0:15:16.97,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But we ain't got no daughters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.36,0:15:20.94,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna toss a ton yer way, Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:20.94,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.56,0:15:24.06,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:25.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru, look! I got mochi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.44,0:15:30.61,MX Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}Fisherman
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.44,0:15:31.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doin', Kenta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.29,0:15:35.34,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just... I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.68,0:15:36.33,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, just get scoopin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.81,0:15:41.58,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Sensei came too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.93,0:15:44.21,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Feelin' a mite better?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.39,0:15:46.01,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You came too, Hiroshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.01,0:15:48.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I was studying, but \Nthese guys dragged me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.91,0:15:51.51,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After he shrewdly grabbed a glove.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.62,0:15:53.63,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm doing anything, \NI'm doing it seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.63,0:15:55.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't gonna lose, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.83,0:15:57.39,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.28,0:16:00.35,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,About before... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:04.36,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? That still got ya down?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.72,0:16:06.57,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry none 'bout us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.57,0:16:09.04,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just focus on pickin' mochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.41,0:16:15.25,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to get a lot, you must keep \Naway from the two professionals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.25,0:16:16.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Professionals"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:18.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The first one is Yasuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:21.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She has long years of \Nmochi-picking experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.20,0:16:23.00,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She always picks the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.36,0:16:25.06,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The other one is Panchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:28.50,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll snatch mochi you've already \Npicked, so stay 'way from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:31.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond that, we just have to show our stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:34.29,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.82,0:16:36.34,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:38.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're throwin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:39.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're pickin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:41.63,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeaaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.63,0:16:42.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:44.81,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get set!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:48.90,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a late start.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:52.45,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go up front to make a catch...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.48,0:17:00.04,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:01.79,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I'll try again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:10.21,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Now's my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.32,0:17:15.40,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.89,0:17:18.01,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You... took my mochi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.34,0:17:23.39,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grr! Is God testing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:24.85,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:26.33,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.33,0:17:28.80,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go at it with your usual guts, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:31.98,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "my usual"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:36.91,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,So in the end, it's the same here too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.80,0:17:40.88,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Some can get them, and some can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.80,0:17:46.71,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than struggle, wouldn't it be \Nmore gracious to stop trying altogether?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.24,0:17:49.72,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll just quit...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:50.74,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,...calligraphy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.83,0:18:01.86,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Panchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.86,0:18:04.34,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get anythin', Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.34,0:18:05.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.71,0:18:08.02,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe yer just bad at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:10.90,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I really am no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:12.32,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:15.82,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good if yer always lookin' up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.33,0:18:19.40,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait patiently...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.40,0:18:22.02,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And take it once it hits the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.59,0:18:26.29,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You find a mess of \Nopportunities fallen below.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:28.29,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Below...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:32.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't many left now, but keep tryin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:33.72,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.72,0:18:36.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do if I still can't get any?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:38.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's some guy better than me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:40.34,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so what if I can't pick mochi at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.77,0:18:43.89,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.15,0:18:47.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At such times...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.92,0:18:50.97,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, "Go on ahead."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.72,0:18:57.38,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let 'er go, and try for a plumper mochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.69,0:19:00.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{If you?}Never quit yieldin' and pickin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.80,0:19:04.49,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And see what y'get!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.07,0:19:08.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.05,0:19:11.17,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry 'fore they're all gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.44,0:19:14.29,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.41,0:19:15.55,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:17.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.77,0:19:28.43,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.35,0:19:34.19,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that really for the best...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:38.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, how many did you pick?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.46,0:19:39.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask, Naru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.96,0:19:41.82,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't pick a single one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.17,0:19:45.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I picked a whole twenty-eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:47.78,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, the grown man got zero...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.78,0:19:50.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I really did pick one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.11,0:19:51.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that Panchi—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.20,0:19:52.21,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.44,0:19:56.59,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.54,0:19:59.77,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet-bean soup?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.77,0:20:01.48,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that'd be Panchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.48,0:20:03.51,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She goes berserk during mochi-pickings,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:06.67,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but afterwards, she drops off food like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.67,0:20:11.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She gets a lot to distribute them to people \Nwho couldn't make it to the picking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.79,0:20:14.62,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, don' lose next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.20,0:20:16.36,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This mochi's all wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.67,0:20:18.77,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one Kenta dropped...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.77,0:20:20.33,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So's one of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.94,0:20:23.28,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with failure...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.84,0:20:25.59,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,today was kinda fun for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:27.81,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.64,0:20:32.43,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Told ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.09,0:22:08.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yer catchin' crayfish too?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.74,0:22:10.38,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Schoolmaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.38,0:22:13.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't look at all like an educator.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.55,0:22:16.00,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Schoolmaster, you observin' crayfish too?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.38,0:22:18.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, why would I?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.13,0:22:20.06,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I use 'em as bait for rock snapper.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.99,0:22:21.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.87,0:22:23.61,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doin', Naru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.00,0:22:25.74,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Usin' crayfish as bait's mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.75,0:22:31.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru, if you allow it, you can eat snapper.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.56,0:22:34.74,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd like some, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.74,0:22:36.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let's catch crayfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.05,0:22:37.81,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Let's fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.81,0:22:40.65,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Schoolmaster, how d'you use them as bait?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.65,0:22:42.00,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, first...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.25,0:22:45.00,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You pull off their claws, like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.20,0:22:45.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.05,0:22:49.15,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Naru!
